ecture-level city|Prefecture-level]] & [[Sub-provincial city]]\n<!-- images and maps ----------->\n| image_skyline           = Dalian Montage (2).jpg\n| image_size              = \n| image_caption           = Clockwise from top: Dalian skyline (Qingniwa [[central business district|CBD]]), Citibank at [[Zhongshan Square (Dalian)|Zhongshan Square]], Dalian International Conference Center, Tiaoyue Bridge at [[Xinghai Square]]\n| image_seal              = \n| image_shield            = \n| nickname                = \n| motto                   = \n| image_map               = {{maplink|frame=yes|plain=yes|type=shape|stroke-width=2|stroke-color=#000000|zoom=7|frame-lat=39.44|frame-long=122.27}}\n| image_map1              = Location of Dalian Prefecture within Liaoning (China).png\n| map_caption1            = Location of Dalian City jurisdiction in Liaoning\n| pushpin_map             = Liaoning\n| pushpin_label_position  = \n| pushpin_map_caption     = Location of the city center in Liaoning\n<!-- Location ------------------>\n| coordinates             = {{coord|38|55|15|N|121|38|21|E|type:adm2nd_region:CN-21|format=dms|display=it}}\n| coor_pinpoint = [[Zhongshan Square (Dalian)|Zhongshan Square]]\n| subdivision_type = Country\n| subdivision_name        = [[China|People's Republic of China]]\n| subdivision_type1       = [[Provinces of China|Province]]\n| subdivision_type2       = \n| subdivision_name1       = [[Liaoning]]\n| subdivision_name2       = \n| established_title       = Settled\n| established_date        = 1899\n| established_title1      = \u2013 [[Treaty of Shimonoseki|Transfer of sovereignty to Japan (Treaty of Shimonoseki)]]\n| established_date1       = 17 April 1895\n| established_title2      = \u2013 [[Russian Dalian|Russian occupation]]<br><br>\u2013 [[Kwantung Leased Territory|Japanese occupation]]\n| established_date2       = 3 March 1898 \u2013 2 January 1905<br>1905 \u2013 15 August 1945\n| established_title3      = \u2013 Transfer of sovereignty to China